   673                                  ;
   674                                  ;       DS,ES,SS -----> 007b00  +-----------------------------------------------+ DS:0000
   675                                  ;                               |  Boot Stack & Boot PSP (Unused)               |
   676                                  ;                               |  256 = 100h bytes                             |
   677                                  ;       SS:SP --------> 007c00  +-----------------------------------------------+ DS:0100  07b0:0100
